      \u003cspan\u003e6 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            Better Image Generation\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDALL-E was a useful AI image generator, but it had numerous issues that needed addressing. For example, it was notoriously bad at creating text; anything more than simple words quickly became a problem.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eThough it occasionally makes errors, GPT-4o is much better at generating images. Humans interact better with objects, and the app listens to prompts more. When coupled with ChatGPT\u0026#39;s editing features, you get a strong all-around AI image generator, though Adobe Firefly is still better.\u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/chatgpt-image-generated.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/chatgpt-image-generated.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/chatgpt-image-generated.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/chatgpt-image-generated.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/chatgpt-image-generated.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/chatgpt-image-generated.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/chatgpt-image-generated.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/chatgpt-image-generated.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/chatgpt-image-generated.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2100\" height=\"1400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Screenshot of Library With a ChatGPT Image Generated in GPT-4o \" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/chatgpt-image-generated.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/chatgpt-image-generated.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eOne annoyance is that even now, GPT-4o sometimes doesn\u0026#39;t listen to requests. Regardless of how many times you reword the prompt, ChatGPT sometimes just won\u0026#39;t do what you asked it to. Hopefully, this will be ironed out with enough time.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"faster-processing\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e5 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            Faster Processing\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI\u0026#39;m what you would describe as a ChatGPT power user, and as a result, I\u0026#39;ve noticed subtle changes, such as increased processing speeds. From what I\u0026#39;ve seen, GPT-4o takes less time to craft responses.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eConversations typically flow much faster, especially when the software doesn\u0026#39;t have to search the web or update memory. The web app could use some improvement, as conversation speeds slow down as they grow, but it\u0026#39;s still significantly better than before.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eSince you can speak more quickly with the tool these days, it\u0026#39;s even easier to \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/chatgpt-time-saving-hacks/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003esave time and accomplish more with ChatGPT\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"offering-more-suggestions\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e4 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            Offering More Suggestions\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEarlier versions of ChatGPT often felt like using the app as a one-sided idea launchpad. You could receive suggestions if you manually prompted the chatbot, but it rarely took the initiative on its own. However, GPT-4o is much better at giving suggestions without you needing to prompt further.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eChatGPT asks if you want to create spreadsheets, images, mind maps, and more. Often, these suggestions will be things that you either didn\u0026#39;t think of or would have needed to spend more time manually working on.\u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/screenshot-2025-05-01-at-11-43-19.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/screenshot-2025-05-01-at-11-43-19.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/screenshot-2025-05-01-at-11-43-19.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/screenshot-2025-05-01-at-11-43-19.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/screenshot-2025-05-01-at-11-43-19.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/screenshot-2025-05-01-at-11-43-19.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/screenshot-2025-05-01-at-11-43-19.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/screenshot-2025-05-01-at-11-43-19.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/screenshot-2025-05-01-at-11-43-19.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2874\" height=\"1398\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"ChatGPT offering suggestions in the app\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/screenshot-2025-05-01-at-11-43-19.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/screenshot-2025-05-01-at-11-43-19.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWhen using Deep Research, ChatGPT often asks follow-up questions to ensure it has all the necessary information. You can tell GPT-4o to stop offering suggestions if you think they\u0026#39;re too much, but having this feature on by default is great for creative thinking.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"better-memorization\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e3 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            Better Memorization\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYou may need to start different conversations on ChatGPT for numerous reasons. Perhaps you want to organize your thoughts more effectively, or maybe you\u0026#39;ve reached the maximum conversation limit.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eRegardless, you don\u0026#39;t need to worry about the app forgetting everything it\u0026#39;s told you. The software can cross-read and extract any relevant information to better inform its responses. Even after deleting certain memories, I\u0026#39;ve found that the tool is capable of understanding the context without me needing to refine my prompt.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eBecause ChatGPT can remember what you tell it more effectively, you\u0026#39;ll receive much better responses than before. This alone is worth paying the monthly price for Plus.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"improved-non-english-use\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e2 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            Improved Non-English Use\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhile ChatGPT has made significant strides in its English-language offerings, it hasn\u0026#39;t always performed as well in other languages. But with GPT-4o, it\u0026#39;s much better in this respect.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eIn addition to English, I sometimes use GPT-4o in Danish. While it\u0026#39;s still not on the same level as English, the tool is better at helping me memorize and develop the responses I want.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eIt could use some improvement in image generation, but I expect that to change in the long run. Languages with special characters will probably take the tool more time to learn.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"better-voice-mode\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e1 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            Better Voice Mode\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIn addition to text-based improvements, ChatGPT\u0026#39;s Voice Mode has made huge strides since the early days of GPT-4o. Conversations flow better, and while you can still tell that you\u0026#39;re talking to a bot, it does feel more human.\u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgpt-monday-voice.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgpt-monday-voice.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgpt-monday-voice.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgpt-monday-voice.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgpt-monday-voice.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgpt-monday-voice.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgpt-monday-voice.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgpt-monday-voice.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgpt-monday-voice.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1675\" height=\"904\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"ChatGPT\u0026#39;s Monday Voice\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgpt-monday-voice.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgpt-monday-voice.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/what-is-chatgpt-monday-voice-mode/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eChatGPT even introduced Monday Mode\u003c/a\u003e, a new voice, in April 2025, to expand its offerings. Besides asking for advice, you can use the tool for interview preparation, to engage in some banter, and much more.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eSince your chats will be transcribed later, it\u0026#39;s worth experimenting with Voice Mode.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eChatGPT Plus offers more benefits than may initially meet the eye, and the significant improvements to GPT-4o are one of those. The free version of ChatGPT is suitable for basic conversations, but you\u0026#39;ll miss out if you don\u0026#39;t upgrade.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
